items.name: Head of Michelangelo's David
items.description: This is a scan from a cast of the original David by Michelangelo, a masterpiece of Renaissance art. The cropped bust was crafted in 1899 (Beckett number 756).  The full statue of David can be downloaded here.

designer.name: SMK - Statens Museum for Kunst
designer.bio: The Statens Museum for Kunst (National Art Museum of Denmark) was founded in 1849 when the Danish royal collections became property of the people. Today we at SMK want to contribute to building a more creative and reflective society that values its history and cherishes difference.

items.name: 3D Print of Head of Michelangelo's David
items.description: Printed in white (monochrome) plaster/gypsum on a ZPrinter 450, infiltrated with bronze. Hand polished, slate black patina applied, light burnishing.
